          "new_post_id": "post_1",
          "new_post_text": "\"Just came across some interesting research from a US university. It looks like microplastics in certain bottled water brands might be linked to hormone imbalances in humans. A 5-year study with 3,000 participants found a significant correlation between drinking bottled water and changes in cortisol and thyroid levels. While the lead researcher says the findings are 'concerning', they're not ready to call it a cause-and-effect yet. Still waiting to hear from health experts on this one.\"",
