          "new_post_text": "\"Just saw this study pop up on my feed... again. It's a study, not a definitive proof. 3,000 participants, 5 years, some correlation found. But we need actual cause-and-effect before calling it a public health crisis. Still waiting on health orgs to chime in. #microplastic #bottledwater\"",
